{"tid":899570,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"周杰倫首做「外景主持」","createTime":"2018-11-12T14:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T14:34:52.000Z","uid":160973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7207e56a56cf1219eee70050994b3ffc8942aac2","tid":899570,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:04:10.000Z","msg":"原來咁多年黎第一次做外景，仲要幫手推埋香港<br />\n<br />\n周董公開的30秒《周遊記》片花預告，片中出現劉德華、五月天、余文樂、林俊傑及蕭敬騰等嘉賓，拍攝足迹遍及海外各大城市。周董3月時在香港，被捕獲和余文樂在知名冰室聚會；8月時又現身台北夜市與黑人等好友大吃小食，相信節目當時已開始拍攝，《周遊記》預計2019年1月播出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PlMb1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PlMb1o&d=zKUfNEAgjCwU09ksVv1QEACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2671a2ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PlMb1o</a>"},{"pid":"dbf318b8b01e39569cec3314a4e6cbc488bde0ea","tid":899570,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef26196b1db9bb26da0c304393bc243a32cfa4a5","tid":899570,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"Jay分別同 陳冠希 余文樂都係好友 其實會唔會尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}